text: Chelsea Lately was a late night comedy talk show by Chelsea Handler on the E! network. Every episode was presented in a half-hour format, and was broadcast Monday through Friday. The final episode of Chelsea Lately aired on August 26, 2014. == Viewers == From 2012 to 2013, viewership went up from 613,000 to 571,000. The live hour-long series finale aired August 26 at 11 pm and was viewed by 1.003 million people. == Awards == Year Result Award Category 2009 Winner Teen Choice Award Choice Late-Night Talk Show 2010 Nominated People's Choice Awards Television Talk Show ==References== == Other websites == * * * * http://www.eonline.com/shows/chelsea_lately Category:2000s American television series Category:American television talk shows Category:American comedy television series Category:English-language television programs
